Definition:
In this tasks you are given a tuple of two terms separated by "
". You have to determine whether the First term is created by the Second term or not. Classify your answers as either "Yes" or "No".

Positive Examples.input:
First term: ghost 
Second term: death
Positive Examples.explanation: It is True since "ghost" is created by "death".

Positive Examples.input:
First term: eat 
Second term: brush teeth
Positive Examples.explanation: It is False since "eat" is not created by "brush teeth".

Negative Examples.input:
First term: go to restaurant 
Second term: park car
Negative Examples.explanation: It is False since "go to restaurant" is not created by "park car". Hence, output "Yes" is incorrect.

Negative Examples.input:
First term: penis 
Second term: vagina
Negative Examples.explanation: It is True since "penis" is created by "vagina". Hence, output "No" is incorrect.
